---
title: Chicken and Savoury Mushroom Sauce with Roasted Brussels Sprouts and Potatoes
description: Nothing says comfort food like pan-roasted chicken breast and a hearty veggie medley of roasted Brussels sprouts and potatoes. Served with a drizzle of a rich mushroom pan sauce, you'll be licking your plate clean!

